title: Infant mortality rate in Yemen 2018
summary: In general Deaths per 1,000 live births has stayed the same over the Year.
Deaths per 1,000 live births is roughly constant from 2014 to 2017.
Maximum Deaths per 1,000 live births, about 42.9 was reported at Year 2014,  2015,  2016, and 2017
Minimum Deaths per 1,000 live births about 42.9 was reached at Year 2014,  2015,  2016, and 2017
